reviewText: It's a really nice story and pretty nicely documented but it's not very long and the video looks like revamped old VHS. Good video if you get it for about 6 or 8 bucks or less.
Amazing story of focus and dedication to purpose.  History truly comes back to life.
I was very happy with the DVD. I have been involved with aircraft maintaince all my life and I enjoyed the movie very much.
Incredible story and a high quality DVD,
